LEGIONELLOSIS, PRISONERS - GERMANY
*************************************
A ProMED post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
[see: Legionellosis, prisoners - Germany 990925100700]
Date: Tue, 5 Oct 1999 09:24:07 +0200
From: "Prof. Dr. Reinier Mutters" <mutters@mailer.uni-marburg.de>

We detected large numbers of _Legionella pneumophila_ serogroup 1 in 3
shower facilities and additionally in different parts of the water system of
the Diez JVA.
